title: How to Retrain Final Layer for New Categories
body_html: Could there be another or newer classification algorithm for image classification like ResNet etc? There are a lot of new neural nets with less classification error than Inception. ImageNet results: http://image-net.org/challenges/LSVRC/2017/results
